# FORM trace caches created by the gen_*_form.wls timing scripts (regenerable; the scripts
# empty their own cache at startup so each run is a clean cold trace).
TraceCache_*form/
# stray TensorBases cache if a script runs with cwd=numtracer (the canonical one is at repo root)
TBCache/

# compile_bench.sh run artifacts (the script + bench/iso TUs are the deliverable, not the outputs)
bench/compile_bench.*.txt
bench/compile_bench.*.report
bench/compile_bench.*.report.json

# Numeric-backend GENERATOR intermediates: the MakeNTKernel "Numeric" path emits a build-time
# generator program (main TU + per-net unit TUs + a decl header) into tests/gen/, compiles+runs it
# to produce the committed straight-line kernels, then the program is disposable. Only the FINAL
# kernels (*_kernel.hh / *_kernels.hh) are the deliverable; these regenerable intermediates were
# ~62 MB of repo bloat. The gen_*.wls SOURCE scripts (different extension) are kept.
tests/gen/gen_*.cpp
tests/gen/gen_*_nets.hh

build*/
